          "content": "---\nname: Bug report\nabout: Report something that is not working as expected\ntitle: \"Bug: \"\nlabels: \"\"\nassignees: \"\"\n---\n\n## Summary\nDescribe the bug and the user impact.\n\n## Steps to Reproduce\n1.\n2.\n3.\n\n## Expected Behavior\nWhat did you expect to happen?\n\n## Actual Behavior\nWhat happened instead?\n\n## Environment\n- Node.js version:\n- npm version:\n- Operating system:\n\n## Additional Context\nAdd screenshots, logs, or links that may help diagnose the problem.\n",
