        {
          "content": "---\nname: Maintenance report\nabout: Request maintenance, cleanup, refactoring, or housekeeping work\ntitle: \"Maintenance: \"\nlabels: \"\"\nassignees: \"\"\n---\n\n## Summary\nDescribe the maintenance work needed.\n\n## Motivation\nWhy is this cleanup, refactor, or housekeeping work valuable?\n\n## Scope\nList the files, modules, or processes that may be affected.\n\n## Validation\nHow should maintainers confirm the maintenance work is complete?\n\n## Additional Context\nAdd links, notes, or constraints.\n",
