      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"{\\\"issues\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":4808715213,\\\"number\\\":2,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Bug: Login form validation not working\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Summary\\\\nThe login form validation is not catching invalid input, and this is important for the authentication flow.\\\\n\\\\n## Impact\\\\nThis is high impact for users trying to sign in and is blocking validation confidence for the login experience.\\\\n\\\\n## Expected Behavior\\\\nInvalid email addresses and missing required fields should show validation messages before submission.\\\\n\\\\n## Actual Behavior\\\\nThe form accepts invalid input without showing the expected validation feedback.\\\\n\\\\n## Environment\\\\n- Node.js project\\\\n- Web login form\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"bug\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Something isn't working\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHUfWw\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"priority-high\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"High priority issue\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd2YA\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"first-time-contributor\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Issue created by first-time contributor\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd4QA\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":1,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:11:29Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:03Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808718206,\\\"number\\\":3,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Epic: Redesign user dashboard interface\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Summary\\\\nRedesign the user dashboard interface to improve navigation, readability, and overall workflow.\\\\n\\\\n## Problem Statement\\\\nThe current dashboard experience is important to improve because users need a clearer view of their core account activity.\\\\n\\\\n## Proposed Solution\\\\nCreate a high quality redesign with updated layout, better information hierarchy, and reusable interface components.\\\\n\\\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\\\n- [ ] Requirements are documented\\\\n- [ ] Design and architecture are reviewed\\\\n- [ ] Implementation plan is complete\\\\n- [ ] Testing and documentation are covered\\\\n\\\\n## Epic Tasks\\\\n\\\\n- [ ] #4 - Task 1: Requirements Analysis\\\\n- [ ] #5 - Task 2: Design and Architecture\\\\n- [ ] #6 - Task 3: Implementation\\\\n- [ ] #7 - Task 4: Testing and Documentation\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"epic\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Large feature requiring multiple sub-tasks\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd1bQ\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"priority-high\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"High priority issue\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd2YA\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":1,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:24Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:53Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808719161,\\\"number\\\":4,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"[SUBTASK] Epic: Redesign user dashboard interface - Task 1: Requirements Analysis\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Related to #3\\\\n\\\\nThis sub-issue was created automatically for epic #3.\\\\nTask 1: Requirements Analysis\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"github-actions\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"enhancement\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"New feature or request\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHUfbg\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:42Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:42Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808719179,\\\"number\\\":5,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"[SUBTASK] Epic: Redesign user dashboard interface - Task 2: Design and Architecture\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Related to #3\\\\n\\\\nThis sub-issue was created automatically for epic #3.\\\\nTask 2: Design and Architecture\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"github-actions\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"enhancement\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"New feature or request\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHUfbg\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:43Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:43Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808719196,\\\"number\\\":6,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"[SUBTASK] Epic: Redesign user dashboard interface - Task 3: Implementation\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Related to #3\\\\n\\\\nThis sub-issue was created automatically for epic #3.\\\\nTask 3: Implementation\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"github-actions\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"enhancement\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"New feature or request\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHUfbg\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:43Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:43Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808719219,\\\"number\\\":7,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"[SUBTASK] Epic: Redesign user dashboard interface - Task 4: Testing and Documentation\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Related to #3\\\\n\\\\nThis sub-issue was created automatically for epic #3.\\\\nTask 4: Testing and Documentation\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"github-actions\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"enhancement\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"New feature or request\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHUfbg\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:44Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:44Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808719962,\\\"number\\\":8,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Weekly maintenance cleanup and refactor\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Summary\\\\nPerform normal weekly maintenance cleanup and refactor work for the project.\\\\n\\\\n## Motivation\\\\nThis medium scope cleanup keeps the codebase tidy and easier to review over time.\\\\n\\\\n## Scope\\\\nReview unused code paths, organize small housekeeping items, and document validation steps.\\\\n\\\\n## Validation\\\\nConfirm normal project checks pass after the cleanup is complete.\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"maintenance\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Maintenance and housekeeping tasks\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd1qQ\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"priority-medium\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Medium priority issue\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd2lw\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"needs-review\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Awaiting review from maintainers\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNYwk88AAAACqHd3zQ\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":1,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:12:56Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:13:26Z\\\"}],\\\"pageInfo\\\":{\\\"endCursor\\\":\\\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNy0wNFQxMToxMjo1NlrPAAAAAR6fPlo=\\\",\\\"hasNextPage\\\":false,\\\"hasPreviousPage\\\":false,\\\"startCursor\\\":\\\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNy0wNFQxMToxMToyOVrPAAAAAR6fK80=\\\"},\\\"totalCount\\\":7}\", \"annotations\": null, \"meta\": null}], \"structuredContent\": null, \"isError\": false}"
